    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 represents the pinnacle of BMW\u2019s naturally aspirated engineering. Powered by the legendary S54B32 3.2L inline-six, the engine features individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS system for optimized valve timing across the rev range, culminating in a visceral 8,000 RPM redline. Power is delivered through a precise six-speed Getrag manual gearbox to an M Variable Differential Lock, providing exceptional mechanical grip. The suspension geometry remains crisp, and the subframe has been inspected for structural integrity. While the exterior displays a light patina commensurate with its mileage, the drivetrain remains robust and responsive, offering a pure analog driving experience with no compromises in mechanical performance.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
