      "description": "This meticulously maintained vehicle strikes the perfect balance between luxury and everyday utility. The exterior retains a deep, glossy luster, accented by well-preserved alloy wheels and only the lightest signs of careful use consistent with its age. Inside, you\u2019ll find a pristine, smoke-free cabin featuring supple leather upholstery with minimal bolstering wear and a fully functional suite of modern technology, from the premium sound system to the responsive dual-zone climate control. Mechanically, the car remains in top form; the engine delivers smooth, consistent power, and the transmission shifts seamlessly through every gear. With a documented service history, recent fluid changes, and tires with plenty of tread remaining, this car is a turn-key solution for its next owner. It is a reliable, handsome driver that looks as impressive in the driveway as it feels on the open road.",
