      "description": "Available is a driver-spec 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine. This unit maintains its mechanical integrity with a recently overhauled Vanos system and a reinforced rear subframe to address common chassis fatigue. The powertrain utilizes individual throttle bodies for exceptional throttle response, sending power through a Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox to the variable M differential. Suspension has been refreshed with polyurethane bushings and Bilstein B6 dampers, preserving the original kinematic excellence of the chassis. While showing minor cosmetic patina, the drivetrain is synchronized and the S54 pulls hard to its 8,000 RPM redline. A mechanically sorted example for the discerning enthusiast.",
